        <h2>Becoming a member of USACS</h2>
        <p>Membership in USACS means access to all that the RU computer science community has to offer. With events ranging from CS Trivia Nights to weekly Hacker Hours and the semiannual HackRU, USACS takes charge of all Rutgers’ biggest CS events.
        </p>
        <p>Our diverse community is one that prospers with growth, and we owe our success to our new members. If you are intrigued by technology, coding, social outings, teaching, or leadership, check out out our full events calendar to get involved with whatever suits you best!
        </p>
